\[d_1 d_2 {\bf E} = \frac{({\bf E}(A\rightarrow D \rightarrow C) - {\bf E}(A\rightarrow D))-({\bf E}(A\rightarrow D) - {\bf E}(A))}{\delta x^1 \delta x^2}\]

