\[\nabla_\mu (A_\alpha B^\beta) 
= B^\beta (\nabla_\mu A_\alpha) + A_\alpha (\nabla_\mu B^\beta) 
= B^\beta (\partial_\mu A_\alpha - A_\gamma \Gamma^\gamma_{\alpha \mu}) + A_\alpha (\partial_\mu B^\beta + B^\gamma \Gamma^\beta_{\mu \gamma}) 
